To install service:

sudo cp psm.worker.service psm.elasticsearch.service /lib/systemd/system
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable psm.worker.service
sudo systemctl enable psm.elasticsearch.service

To start/stop service:

sudo systemctl start psm.[worker|elasticsearch].service
sudo systemctl stop psm.[worker|elasticsearch].service
sudo systemctl restart psm.[worker|elasticsearch].service
sudo service apache2 restart

To check status:

sudo systemctl status psm.[worker|elasticsearch].service
